Environment:
    OS  Debian
    gcc 4.8.3
    GNU make 4.0

Language:
    C

Directory tree and file list:
    because the path is hard coded in makefile and some python codes, 
    you have to make sure the directory tree is the same to guarantee 
    proper program behavior. 
    
    /                   : root folder of all programs and data
    /Readme             : this file
    /Report.pdf         : HW2 report
    /48_idx_chr.map_b   : mapping file
    /label/             : label file of training data
    /fbank/             : fbank feature
    /mfcc/              : mfcc feature
    /feature/           : extracted feature
    /src/svm-c/         : svm_struct source code

Usage:
    $ make
    $ make run
